{"tid":1572354,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（幫我推）懷手共黨想搞撚碎個司法制度，製造機會將被捕者消失！","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T04:49:43.000Z","uid":91666,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a11287a34f20a0bb7980979fb9832ae52bfa929","tid":1572354,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"今日咁樣唔同地方大搜捕.又安排d 藍屍打人，推高手捉情緒，製造濫捕機會！跟住又話休班警等到手足返到屋企先拉,唔撚怪得派棍啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被捕人數大幅增加，9嗡話隊爆咗司法機構！777就好似路透社咁會下放權力比警犬可以即時入罪！<br />\n<br />\n唔洗過堂就送撚晒去新屋嶺或者車上支拿無人知.怪唔撚知得咁撚順攤撒回啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重痴撚線過64"},{"pid":"7179397ee118a2701823c74d1758e481e4bbdb7e","tid":1572354,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a4b72afba5fc7163fcc5dc1270ea317d78990e2","tid":1572354,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40f3e89df0d0fc36d669a10f8a85a2c94d3474dc","tid":1572354,"uid":304663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e8a80ea1442c6dcb0473ed2342eed58aa51453f","tid":1572354,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:19:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"593bd413c07c219a9c7d805688ce61dea0096308","tid":1572354,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5345d2f797a2957c7d9564710cf3e64ac2827d2b","tid":1572354,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25b1097bad96374f97c1b88cf637a523f61f65e7","tid":1572354,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:27:09.000Z","msg":"［極重要］全民錫春袋！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572107</a><br